text: Bottle Squad with a boom we are ready to zoom
Bottle Squad!
Bottle Squad ! Be strong,
Be brave,
Be smart,
Be kind

We are the closest friends you’ll ever find.
Bottle Squad
Ba Ba Bottle Squad
Humpty Dumpty

Humpty Dumpty Sat on a wall!
Humpty Dumpty had a great fall.
All the king’s horses and all the king’s men Couldn’t put Humpty together again.
“Baba boom, we are ready to zoom”

Humpty dumpty’s back on the wall
Humpty dumpty says “I won’t fall!”

If you fall down, then you might break!
If you fall down, you’ll have a headache!

Humpty dumpty is propped on the wall.
Humpty dumpty please don’t fall.

The power pets will catch you below,
While the Bottle Squad plays, and puts on a show!

Humpty Dumpty sat on a chair 
The babies took a lot of care

To make sure that he does’nt fall
As he watched them play volley ball

“We power up, and don’t give up!
That’s our Ba-Ba-Promise to you!”
